description: Endi Corp. provides asset management and internet access services. The company's asset management services include fund management services; and operational, marketing, and investor relations support services to niche fund managers. It also provides consumer and business-grade internet access and web hosting services; wholesales managed modems; resells third-party software; and offers various ancillary services in the United States and Canada. The company was founded in 2021 and is based in Richmond, Virginia.
